column5: Nice! Way to go guys!  Cant wait for my first big ski, my big ugli smile probably wont fir in the picture???  Looks like a nice evening on the lake too!
Little late in the day but nice fish made it all good!

Little late in the day but nice fish made it all good! Yeah we work odd hours.  Our goal was walleye but we found a few spots that looked good and well as you can tell worked out.  Went out again last night the same time 7 - 10pm and found 2 muskies surfacing and showing off their fin and tail but not willing to play...  I'm sure the one was this very fish posted above.
